 See the attached screenshot.

fields.description:
There are two related but separate issues issues affecting HE and TAFE applications from course pages. 

Basically, when affected users click through from a course page, they are then required to select the course they are applying for from a list of available courses. It should be automatically selected from the URL.

The issue affecting HE applications only affects applicants who are already logged in to Admissions Centre.

The issue affecting TAFE applications affects all applications from the website.

Updating to the proposed URLs appears to resolve both issues.


Current URLs:

- TAFE: https://gotovu.custhelp.com/app/tafe/landing?c_code=CHC50413
- HE: http://gotovu.custhelp.com/app/launch_application?c_code=ABAB


Proposed URLs:

- TAFE: https://gotovu.custhelp.com/app/tafe/launch_application?c_code=CHC50413
- HE: https://gotovu.custhelp.com/app/launch_application?c_code=ABAB

(Note the course codes above are suitable for testing, but are examples only. The issues apply to any open courses.)
fields.summary: Fix Admissions Centre URLs
